      "content": "but thats the thing. i've tried the \"small steps\" thing. i've tried the therapy, the habits, the small changes. it never actually stays changed. it's like there's this gravity that just pulls me back into the same hole every time. i'm just exhausted from fighting a battle that i'm clearly destined to lose. it feels like the loop is the only thing that's actually real.",
